column5: Evenin Folks, Headin up to quinte saturday morning down near carrying place. I need to get minnows and will be coming through around 6 630 does anyone know if someone is open at that time round them parts
Try Skevys, I called them on Saturday afternoon to ask what time they open on Sunday.  Ron said he had a guy coming in a t 5am, so it may be the same for this weekend.
